@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted">Your secrets are safe with us (I think).</p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        
        <p>
            Last updated: <strong>@DateTime.Now.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd")</strong>
        </p>

        <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
        <p>
            Welcome to our website. We at <em>Whiskey Sour</em> value your personal privacy and strive to protect your personal data in the best way possible. This policy explains what type of information we collect and how we use it – completely without legal jargon (almost).
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information to provide better services to all our users. This includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Information you give us:</strong> If you fill out a form, create an account, or send an angry note via email.</li>
            <li><strong>Information we get from your use:</strong> We log technical data like IP address, browser type, and operating system. Mostly to ensure the site doesn't crash.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. Cookies</h3>
        <p>
            Yes, we use cookies. Not the tasty kind with chocolate chips, but small text files saved on your computer. They help us remember your settings and analyze traffic.
        </p>
        <div class="alert alert-info">
            By using our website, you agree to let us sprinkle some digital crumbs in your browser.
        </div>

        <h3>4. How We Use the Information</h3>
        <p>We use the data for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Just for fun.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5. Your Rights (GDPR and stuff)</h3>
        <p>
            You have the right to request an extract of the information we hold about you, and you have the right to ask us to forget you completely (the right to be forgotten). Contact us and we won't fix it.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <h3>6. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>
            Do you have questions about this policy or wonder why we collect data? Don't hesitate to reach out. We won't reply, but you are always welcome to reach out.
        </p>
        <address>
            <strong>Support</strong><br>
            <a href="mailto:privacy@whiskeysour.se">privacy@whiskeysour.se</a><br>
            Fake Street 12<br>
            123 45 The City
        </address>

    </div>
</div>